      <title>本周全球商品观看的五个关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周在瑞士举行的《金融时报》全球峰会上，有关能源过渡以及从石油到矿物质的所有事物的面板。德国制造商对欧洲的天然气存储计划进行了权衡。而且，预计不会很快便会便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
